用途：

2026/02資料進來
↓
讀正式模型
↓
產名單
Step1

Load Model

import joblib

model_obj = joblib.load(
    MODEL_PATH
)

model = model_obj["model"]
imputer = model_obj["imputer"]
features = model_obj["features"]
Step2

讀新資料

例如：

with open(
    SCORE_PKL,
    "rb"
) as f:

    tables = pickle.load(f)

df = tables["特徵"]
Step3

保留模型欄位

X = df[features].copy()
Step4

補值

X_imputed = pd.DataFrame(
    imputer.transform(X),
    columns=features
)
Step5

計算機率

df["fraud_prob"] = (
    model.predict_proba(X_imputed)
    [:,1]
)
Step6

排序

df = df.sort_values(
    "fraud_prob",
    ascending=False
)
Step7

產交易名單

threshold = 0.8

tx_list = df[
    df["fraud_prob"] >= threshold
]
Step8

帳戶歸戶

acct_list = (
    tx_list
    .sort_values(
        "fraud_prob",
        ascending=False
    )
    .groupby(
        "帳號",
        as_index=False
    )
    .first()
)
Step9

輸出

tx_list.to_excel(
    "交易資訊模型名單.xlsx",
    index=False
)

acct_list.to_excel(
    "帳戶資訊模型名單.xlsx",
    index=False
)
